@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home - Frank's Restaurant";
    ViewData["Description"] = "Founded in 1976, Frank's Restaurant has been family-owned and operated for over four decades.";
    ViewData["ShowMenuButton"] = "true";
}

@Html.Partial("_Hero")


<div class="container mt-5">
    <h2 class="text-center">About Us</h2>
    <p class="lead text-center">At Frank's, we pride ourselves on offering top-notch comfort food and a welcoming atmosphere for all. Family-owned and operated for over 50 years!</p>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>About Our Restaurant</h3>
            <p>Frank's has worked hard to serve the Jackson Lake area for almost 50 years. Our menu has a wide range of dishes, so with a meal for every appetite the only requirement is that you come hungry.</p>

            <p>  Frank’s Restaurant was started by Frank Castellana along with his wife Marie Castellana after moving businesses of his own, Split T and Self Service, from Northwest Atlanta on Simpson Street. Frank’s Restaurant has been a fixture in Covington for 44 years. If was first started in 1970 on Highway 36 in Covington beside Frank’s One Stop until it was destroyed by fire in 1973. After the destruction the restaurant was moved to its current site located on Highway 212. The restaurant was started with 2 rooms and has grown substantially over the past 40 years into the largest restaurant in the City of Covington, GA. The last remodeling was done over the past 8 years adding a full sports bar with flat screen televisions in every room with a full bar to match.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/images/Frank-Castellana-Family.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Family Picture" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h2 class="text-center">What We Offer</h2>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <img src="~/images/Franks-Pizza.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Pizza" style="height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Signature Pizza</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Enjoy our freshly made signature pizzas with the finest ingredients and the perfect crust!</p>
                    <a class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" asp-controller="Menu" asp-action="Index">See Menu</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <img src="~/images/Franks-Fried-Food.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Fried Food" style="height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Crispy Fried Favorites</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">From crispy fried chicken to fried seafood, our fried dishes are a fan favorite!</p>
                    <a class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" asp-controller="Menu" asp-action="Index">See Menu</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <img src="~/images/Franks-Bar-Entrance.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Bar Entrance" style="height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Relax at the Bar</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Join us at the bar for a refreshing drink and great conversation in a relaxing environment.</p>
                    <a class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" asp-controller="Menu" asp-action="Index">See Menu</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


